  "recommended_next_step": "Implement a small pure-function continuity synthesis primitive with tests proving deterministic output, stable status precedence, fail-closed unknown statuses, input immutability, explicit missing-evidence findings, and absence of filesystem/network/provider/dispatch/approval/execution/lifecycle/replay/sidepanel/orchestration/persistence/semantic-autonomy behavior."
